I interviewed Chef Daniel, a professional chef who provides catering services for weddings, birthday parties, corporate events, and family gatherings.

His target audience includes families, businesses, and event organizers looking for quality catering services.

Chef Daniel wanted a modern and professional website with warm colors that reflect food and hospitality. He wanted the website to showcase his services, featured dishes, and contact information.

The main goal of the website is to attract potential customers and encourage them to make bookings for catering services.
